title: Introduction to Superstarch
content: Superstarch is a product derived from corn starch that is used to improve athletic performance. It is produced by Generation UCAN. In this post, Peter Attia explains the evolution of sports nutrition products and how Superstarch is a step-function improvement over all existing products. He also shares a video explaining how our bodies use stored energy to generate motion.

title: Interview with a Prolific Trainer
content: In Part II of the post, Peter Attia shares an interview with one of the most prolific trainers of professional athletes who has transformed his training with Superstarch. The trainer has also used Superstarch to train some of the highest profile athletes in the country.

title: Revolutionizing Sports Nutrition
content: Superstarch was originally developed to save the lives of children with a very rare genetic disorder. However, Peter Attia believes that this technology is going to revolutionize sports nutrition as we know it.
